| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-6032 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: aaf5a1e5-cf4e-58c1-85d9-91065d014797"
